===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} ''[[salmoun#Middle English|salmoun, samoun]]'' from {{etyl|xno}} ''[[saumon#Anglo-Norman|saumon]]'' from {{etyl|fro}} ''[[saumon#Old French|saumon]]'' from {{etyl|la}} {{term|salmo|salmō, salmōn-|salmon|lang=la}}. Displaced native {{enm}} ''[[lax#Middle English|lax]]'' "salmon" from {{etyl|ang|-}} ''[[leax#Old English|leax]]''.

===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|pl2=salmon}}

# {{italbrac|plural '''salmon'''}} One of [[several]] [[specie]]s of [[fish]] of the [[Salmonidae]] family.
